						<summary>

						<p>This inscription is damaged and built in at the end. It records the deposit of 20 <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> of gold for providing food offerings to the god Kūttāḍumdēvar <hi rend="italic">[Naṭarāja].</hi> The measure <hi rend="italic">Parakēsari-nāḻi</hi> is mentioned.</p>						

